<div class="flex flex-col items-center font-oswald h-screen">
  <header>
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bebasneue font-bold m-5 text-center"> einwortspiel </h2>
  </header>

  <main class = "grow flex flex-col justify-evenly md:w-3/4 lg:w-3/5 xl:w-1/2 2xl:w-2/5">
    <div class = "flex justify-center"> 
      <.form :let={f} for={%{"language" => "de"}} action={~p"/table/create"} class="flex flex-col justify-evenly items-center text-center gap-4 w-full"> 
        <.button class="text-2xl font-semibold font-bebasneue pt-3 pb-2 px-3 m-2">
          Play
        </.button>

        <fieldset class="bg-white p-4 rounded-sm">
          <h4 class="text-xl mb-2 font-bebasneue"> Game Language </h4>
          <ul class="items-center">
          <li class="inline m-0.5">
          <.input field={f[:language]}
            id="lang_de"
            type="radio"
            label="German"
            value="de"
            {%{"checked" => true}}
          />
          </li>
          <li class="inline m-0.5">
          <.input field={f[:language]}
            id="lang_en"
            type="radio"
            label="English"
            value="en"
          />
          </li>
          </ul>
        </fieldset>

      </.form>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col justify-evenly gap-4">
    <div class = "rounded-sm bg-white p-1.5 md:p-2" >
      <h4 class="text-center font-bebasneue text-xl mb-2"> The Game </h4>
      <p> Each player gets three words, which have to be described by a single clue. Two of those three words are the same for all players, the remaining word is different. Based on the clues of the other players, everybody has to find the word that they alone have.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class = "rounded-sm bg-white p-1.5 md:p-2" >
      <h4 class="text-center font-bebasneue text-xl mb-2"> How To Play </h4>
      <ol class="list-decimal list-inside">
      <li> Set the language for the game and press play to create a game table. </li>
      <li> Invite other players by sharing the URL. </li>
      <li> Start playing. </li>
      </ol>
    </div>
    </div>

    
  </main>

  <footer class="m-2">
    <small>
      <dl class="grid grid-flow-col auto-cols-max justify-center items-center" >
      <dt class="col-start-1 justify-self-end" >
        <div class="w-3.5 h-3.5">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="feather feather-mail"><path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"></path><polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"></polyline></svg></div> 
      </dt> <dd class="col-start-2 justify-self-start ml-1.5"> marcel.wienoebst (AT) gmx.de </dd>
      <dt class="col-start-1 justify-self-end">
        &copy;
      </dt> <dd class="col-start-2 justify-self-start ml-1.5"> <%= Map.fetch!(DateTime.utc_now, :year)  %> Marcel Wien√∂bst. All rights reserved. </dd>
      </dl>
    </small>
  </footer>
</div>
